Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我也从这边上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再坚持一会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,开炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,千冬姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(129.333,106)\fad(0,400)}一夏的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就已经天亮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉 你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哼哼 今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是裸体喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是采用了我优秀副官的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是开了那副官比较好 真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我在这等着你醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,「在夏日的结尾庙会约会」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fs15\be1\frz8.378\3c&HA87EF1&\pos(164.053,197.886)}马上让两人擦出\N爱的火花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正大标宋_GBK\blur0.5\bord0\fs15\c&H2C2E34&\pos(452.906,129.64)}New rainbow island
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不是今年刚建好的娱乐游泳池举办的活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想去那玩玩来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在庙会那边的广场上还有出租浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要穿浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和你独处的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那去吧 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了嘛 怎么生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐 暑假在英国工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我身为奥卢卡多家族的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是做了理所应当之事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,总算是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是想和所念之人共处同一片天空之下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一…一夏同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一周没见了 贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,难道因为想我特地出来迎接的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想到塞西莉亚要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我就迫不及待的想见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏同学 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事 只是坐久了站起来有点晕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 明天一起去这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和一夏同学一起外出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我塞西莉亚·奥卢卡多 定会做好万全的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 他作为我新娘的自觉性实在不足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了吗 劳拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,额 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 劳拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有空的话 去买衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么 衣服的话军队配发的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那是军装啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着这个出门的话 本国人会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你想 暑假也快结束了 一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那十点左右出来如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如何 我换外出用的衣服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是选了校服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 呐 知道临海公园神奇可丽饼的传闻吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,和喜欢的人一起喝MIX-BERRY味的可丽饼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱就能够成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过听说总是会卖完诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,让恋爱成功的MIX BERRY？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好冰~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~ 明天暑假就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,最后这天真希望能和一夏留下夏日的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 我都没回国留在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这小子一次都没有来邀我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉 你觉得裙子和裤子哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跟我说无所谓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,话说劳拉你这一点和一夏很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,夫妇很像是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,秋装我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是夏天 秋天的衣服秋天再买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可是女孩子一般都是先准备好下一季的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,的确 战争了再调整装备和军队已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧 那按顺序看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,银发与金发……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果方便的话 试穿下新款怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有点薄 会不会比较透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉觉得怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯… 白色吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也不错 但是现在穿的就是这颜色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,难得来试穿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 有点麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我对这种事不怎么清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对异性来说这衣服毫无魅力吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太荒谬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都要试 能穿可爱一点的衣服就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那样一夏就会夸奖我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉 那衣服真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只有衣服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 劳拉是最可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 劳拉 换好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,诶? 还穿着校服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 难道不合意么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不 虽说不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再稍微可爱点的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了 要可爱一点的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那具体要怎么样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 暴露一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,像妖精一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,连鞋子都准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有点出乎意料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,难得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\an8}是不是照下来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\an8}我也要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,吾未知胜人之法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只知胜己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要守护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,重要之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部好像又变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,箒 在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,箒 我找你好久了 现在有空吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微等下 有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 你在淋浴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,比起那个有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,时间比较急 不用勉强去也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要我去也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有点累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,难得的嘛 就那样穿出来不久好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个… 什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,弄脏了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,难道第一次穿要留给一夏看么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不是这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要打工吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我是管家的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为比起周围那些男生 你更加帅气漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以穿女仆服就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,果然我是这样风格嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧 十分适合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到 cafe@cruise
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位是点红茶的客人?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么需要的话 请随意吩咐 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,全都给我别动!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别吵!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖投降吧 重复一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想要人质安全的话 给我去准备辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当然别给我装跟踪器和发信机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 全吓成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那边的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我口渴了 给我拿菜单来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 喝下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你喝的下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 你这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看我收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜 不是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,目标2 镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 目标3 镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,被开玩笑 被你们这群小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真慢 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 女仆小姐 管家先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉 我们被发现是代表候补生的话会有些麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 那我们就先撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要是被抓去坐牢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还不如全部给我炸飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,将军!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还要来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再来 就打飞你那双手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们买两个可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要mix-berry的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 今天mix-berry的已经卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉 要点些别的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给我草莓味和蓝莓味的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次吃可丽饼 觉得很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下次和一夏来吃的时候有mix-berry就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,劳 劳拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,干 干干干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你脸上蘸着果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就 就就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你两手都没空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 不要这样生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来 给你吃一口我的可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那家可丽饼店本来是没有mix-berry口味的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,菜单上是没有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 厨房也没有看见类似的果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得还真仔细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 还是吃到mix-berry味了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 草莓和蓝莓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 一直都会卖完的mix-berry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有着这样的玄机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果和男友一起吃的话会很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是睡衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉 这跟你很搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别抱过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哼哼 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,猫一定要在大腿上老实呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好难得的机会 说声喵来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 我非要做这种事情不可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛来嘛 说说看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喵 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,劳拉 太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,黑猫和白猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉两个凑在一起很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔穿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对了对了 关于明天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在6D区域确认入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以最快速度进行迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,重复 在6D区域确认入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急 尽快迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,听好 你的身体里被注入了监视用的纳米机器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请按照命令执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还叫我不能杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子 M
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肉身就想对抗IS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被封印在这基地里的IS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite Stratos 我接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,展开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沉默的西风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,326)}Silent Zephyrus
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说 是亡国机业
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏这家伙积极得不同寻常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,邀请我约会居然都那么害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真是拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.67,0:23:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,难得出去 还想叫上弹他们一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,结果他们好像有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,满怀期待的我真是太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}玩弄少女心的行为是最差劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然也想过会是这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}老婆失格
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.94,0:23:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧去泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.94,0:23:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快点去泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.28,0:24:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早就先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说 我们也快点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}快点…快点…快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊 你那么想去游泳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.12,0:24:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.82,0:24:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,居然给大家都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽气啊 塞西莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.90,0:24:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.40,0:24:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是塞西莉亚人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来没看见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.34,0:24:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.88,0:24:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话 分成两路去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.29,0:25:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,果然夏天游泳是最棒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.03,0:25:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就没看见大家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.33,0:25:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真的都已经来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.18,0:25:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Σ( ° △ °|||)︴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.29,0:25:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.50,0:25:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.81,0:25:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那两人到底去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这边也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.11,0:25:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那去那边找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.79,0:25:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,突然做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.64,0:25:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太险了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.43,0:25:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,发现织斑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.18,0:25:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,随便君 大家都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.12,0:25:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,IS学园的人来了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.23,0:25:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,队长 塞西穿着色色的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.97,0:25:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.95,0:26:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 真大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.97,0:26:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉亚好色
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.43,0:26:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.95,0:26:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.44,0:26:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.16,0:26:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.44,0:26:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.08,0:26:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.99,0:26:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有双人滑水道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.90,0:26:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.76,0:26:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.45,0:26:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让我陪你一起也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.39,0:26:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,箒好狡猾 用猜拳来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.95,0:27:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.44,0:27:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.00,0:27:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 现在开始双人滑水道的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.22,0:27:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,先请男的坐在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.09,0:27:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后女生坐在他两腿之间
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.04,0:27:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.56,0:27:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后男生先这样抱住女生
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.87,0:27:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱紧点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.43,0:27:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 夏露可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.62,0:27:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,随时都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.16,0:27:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.85,0:27:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.77,0:27:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…再抱紧点 不然很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.05,0:27:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 请走好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.11,0:28:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.28,0:28:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.70,0:28:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.84,0:28:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏真色
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.97,0:28:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是故意的 是不可抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.08,0:28:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.87,0:28:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.42,0:28:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.94,0:28:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 现在开始双人滑水道的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.31,0:28:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,先请男的坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.03,0:28:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然后女生坐在他两腿之间
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.05,0:28:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,男生抱住女生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.25,0:28:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,箒 能坐我后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.09,0:28:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不是反了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.47,0:29:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.50,0:29:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,滑的时候水压很大
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.87,0:29:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在我背后会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.43,0:29:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.09,0:29:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.38,0:29:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再贴紧点会安全一点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.21,0:29:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.54,0:29:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请走好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.67,0:29:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看 速度很快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.26,0:29:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 哪里弄疼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.03,0:29:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.81,0:29:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…你的背变宽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.53,0:29:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,背怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.92,0:29:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 快点来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.91,0:30:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底要坐几次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.25,0:30:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 到这种地方来还遇见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.92,0:30:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑老师
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.26,0:30:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不去一夏他们那边没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.13,0:30:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是姐弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.16,0:30:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,难的的休假 和他们碰面就白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.41,0:30:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.27,0:30:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.99,0:30:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 有急事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.81,0:30:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.18,0:31:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.58,0:31:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你第一次见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.79,0:31:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个叫捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.87,0:31:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个把金鱼捞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.75,0:31:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.12,0:31:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 教我怎么玩
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.78,0:31:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.66,0:31:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.23,0:31:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.57,0:31:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,按顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.93,0:31:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.04,0:31:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话就算失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.26,0:31:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.29,0:31:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.16,0:31:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.00,0:31:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,章鱼还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.00,0:31:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(268.944,326)}Devil Fish
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.34,0:31:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃章鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.34,0:31:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(330.787,326)}Octopus
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.03,0:31:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,者可是日本的传统料理
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.20,0:31:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.13,0:31:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来尝尝 劳拉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.70,0:31:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这的确不错
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.76,0:31:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.24,0:31:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那轮到我喂箒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.86,0:31:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.18,0:31:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 张嘴 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.19,0:32:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,狙击我可是无人能敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.79,0:32:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是玩具枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.95,0:32:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.15,0:32:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我很擅长这个
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.88,0:32:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我在军队里 也接受过射击训练哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.09,0:32:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,箒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.75,0:32:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.29,0:32:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的射击水平提高了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.94,0:32:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是近战型
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.44,0:32:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.88,0:32:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以射击不行也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.35,0:32:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.70,0:32:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.26,0:32:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我一定要打下它
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.83,0:32:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我来掩护你 劳拉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.64,0:32:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.74,0:32:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就此一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.42,0:33:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也要参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.14,0:33:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,列队
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,齐射
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.57,0:33:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.43,0:33:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.48,0:34:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天也结束了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.29,0:34:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到我更识楯无登场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.28,0:38:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.24,0:38:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱☆含片
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.24,0:38:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,326)}心灵·镇痛剂
Comment: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== OP ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}きっと会えるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:30.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔と涙を抱いて  君と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:47.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明日の空は  何色に変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:53.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自分の力で　輝かせて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:58.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}知らない事　だからドキドキするね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:05.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}試したい もっと 限界は決めなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:10.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}気付いて　風の声が教える
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:15.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}進もう 次の物語へと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽ばたいて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}負けそうでも逃げたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:27.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と刻む時を 信じて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:33.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔と涙を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:39.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大切な人　守るために強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们一定能够再相见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:30.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你一起分享欢喜 分担悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:47.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明天的天空会是什么颜色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:53.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠自己的力量将它变得闪耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:58.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为是未知的事物 所以才让人如此期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:05.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要尝试更多 不用给自己划好界限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:10.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}风儿自然会告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:15.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向前吧 开始自己的下一段故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}展翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即便遇到坎坷挫折 也不要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:27.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}相信与你共度的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸怀希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:33.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不忘苦与乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:39.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了守护珍爱的人而变坚强吧
Comment: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== ED ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.20,0:34:49.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}高くもっと! BEAUTIFUL SKY 透き通る眼差しへ
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.15,0:34:56.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}守りたい輝きが今日もチカラになるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.29,0:35:15.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}並んだ風にキミを感じる　存在がうれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:26.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}深呼吸して見上げる空は　毎日違う顔なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.03,0:35:32.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}どこまでも行けるね　描いてくここから
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:38.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}昨日より強い自分でいたい　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.20,0:35:45.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}高くもっと! BEAUTIFUL SKY 透き通る眼差しに
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.17,0:35:49.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この瞬間を焼きつけていく
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.87,0:35:55.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}光れもっと! BEAUTIFUL SKY 翼ごと抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.81,0:36:03.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}守りたい輝きが今日もチカラをくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.20,0:34:49.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在那美丽的天空中飞得更高 向往着那透彻的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.15,0:34:56.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}想守护的光辉今天也会成为我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.29,0:35:15.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}随着风奔跑让我感到 你的存在令我十分开心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:26.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一口深呼吸后抬头仰望天空空 每天都是不同的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.03,0:35:32.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}让我们从这里开始 直到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:38.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}不论何时 都想成为比昨天更坚强的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.20,0:35:45.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在那美丽的天空中飞得更高 用那透彻的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.17,0:35:49.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}把这个瞬间铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.87,0:35:55.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在那美丽的天空中更加闪耀  连翅膀一直拥抱在怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.81,0:36:03.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}想守护的光辉今天也给我来了力量
